{"1":[[29,222,"Hiring Daughter-in-Law: High Salary."],[228,414,"Only the tough need apply!"],[1772,1864,"Greetings, Mrs. Johnson."],[1864,2044,"Good day, Mrs. Johnson."],[2044,2228,"How are the two girls who passed"],[2240,2352,"yesterday getting along"],[2360,2484,"with Graham and Colton?"],[2564,2640,"Mrs. Johnson,"],[2660,2748,"see for yourself."],[2770,2876,"Mrs. Johnson,"],[2916,3088,"if we'd known your two sons"],[3104,3224,"had such weird tempers,"],[3241,3560,"we wouldn't be caught dead interviewing here!"],[3562,3642,"Hey, wait..."],[3812,3936,"After all, the Johnsons are"],[3936,4124,"one of the four elite families in Yestar."],[4168,4324,"But neither of my sons"],[4324,4453,"has a wife."],[4524,4652,"I can't even hold my head up"],[4652,4816,"in front of those rich socialites."],[4816,4928,"Don't be too sad, Mrs. Johnson."],[5048,5228,"Mr. Graham is withdrawn,"],[5284,5408,"rarely speaks,"],[5478,5610,"and doesn't let women touch him."],[5804,5988,"Mr. Colton is a playboy who loves trouble,"],[6004,6156,"partying with his sketchy friends every day,"],[6208,6324,"and hardly ever comes home."],[6460,6540,"Mr. Graham and Mr. Colton"],[6564,6640,"are really not men"],[6640,6748,"that ordinary girls can handle."],[6844,6940,"But the problem is,"],[6940,7080,"they can't keep going on like this."],[7096,7336,"The Johnsons have hundreds of billions in assets,"],[7336,7460,"and someone has to inherit it."],[7552,7792,"If heaven could send me two daughters-in-law"],[7844,7944,"to help me straighten out"],[7944,8092,"these two brats, it would be great."],[8105,8352,"Yeah! That was amazing!"],[9136,9216,"Bravo!"],[10520,10600,"Everyone,"],[10600,10716,"was my sister amazing just now?"],[10728,10880,"-So awesome! -She was great!"],[10900,11008,"So, do you guys want"],[11008,11148,"to see something even better?"],[11152,11424,"-One more! -One more!"],[12863,12977,"-Alright! -One more!"],[12980,13120,"That's all for today's show!"],[13120,13224,"Thank you, everyone!"],[13360,13520,"These two girls aren't bad."],[13536,13692,"One is a smooth talker,"],[13692,13820,"and the other has impressive skills."],[13860,14036,"Aren't they exactly who I'm seeking?"]],"2":[[540,688,"Didn't we agree on 600 for the gig?"],[688,804,"Why are you only giving us 200?"],[819,899,"600?"],[910,1012,"Have you seen the cr*p you two"],[1012,1104,"call a performance?"],[1120,1168,"600?"],[1188,1280,"Giving you 200"],[1292,1420,"is me being generous."],[1432,1596,"But the crowd clearly loved it!"],[1628,1740,"I saw them going into the store to buy..."],[1788,1892,"Quit your whining."],[1892,1940,"Keep this up,"],[1956,2056,"and I'll call the cops"],[2056,2184,"to report you for causing trouble."],[2192,2308,"You won't even get the 200."],[2316,2412,"Say that again?"],[2748,2892,"Let it go, sister."],[2932,3108,"He's not worth dirtying your hands."],[3136,3264,"A crooked merchant like you is"],[3264,3372,"only out here harming society"],[3404,3596,"because prenatal care has gotten too good."],[3596,3632,"You"],[3644,3716,"Don't \"you\" me."],[3732,3876,"What you need to do right now,"],[3876,4016,"is go home, lock the doors,"],[4016,4092,"turn on the gas,"],[4092,4188,"and take a nice, long nap!"],[4220,4285,"Or,"],[4336,4424,"find a building to jump off,"],[4472,4704,"and help the people lower housing prices."],[4948,4988,"Let's go."],[5116,5386,"Argh!"],[5596,5712,"Sigh."],[5808,6056,"What doesn't kill me"],[6096,6300,"just keeps beating me up."],[6320,6576,"My future is so bleak."],[6596,6724,"So refreshing."],[6796,7060,"Life is full of twists and turns."],[7144,7288,"It's really cheap."],[7311,7527,"Sigh."],[8117,8237,"What should we do?"],[8283,8448,"We grew up in an orphanage,"],[8448,8576,"and the director raised us"],[8576,8681,"like her own granddaughters."],[8696,8884,"But now, the orphanage is out of funds."],[8908,9084,"The kids barely have enough to eat."],[9096,9196,"And yet, right now,"],[9196,9320,"we can't help at all."],[9364,9420,"It's okay."],[9432,9612,"I'll sell our e-bike in a few days,"],[9612,9776,"along with the pots and pans."],[9812,9980,"That'll help her get by for a few more days."],[10004,10064,"OK."],[10212,10308,"Young ladies,"],[10488,10656,"are you in urgent need of money?"],[10700,10820,"I have a job offer here."],[10848,10920,"The pay is"],[10920,11132,"100 times what you make now."],[11448,11520,"What do you think?"],[11560,11724,"Would you like to consider it?"],[11744,11964,"Professional Daughter-in-Law for the rich."],[11996,12084,"That's right."],[12104,12392,"Become a professional daughter-in-law for the Johnsons."],[12404,12600,"You don't have to fulfill marital duties,"],[12613,12741,"or have children."],[12828,13056,"You'll also receive a monthly salary."],[13104,13220,"Every morning when you wake up,"],[13260,13340,"you'll be"],[13340,13518,"in a 5,000-square-foot mansion,"],[13540,13672,"with free service"],[13692,13840,"from chauffeurs and maids."],[14752,14884,"If it were really that good,"],[14904,15052,"people would be fighting to get in."],[15052,15180,"Yeah."],[15180,15360,"Why would you need to come find us?"],[15364,15407,"Well..."],[16048,16222,"You ladies might not know this,"],[16240,16408,"but our two young masters' tempers"],[16432,16629,"might be a little tricky to handle."],[16744,16920,"Tricky?"],[17404,17500,"The Young Masters are here."],[17508,17624,"You'll see for yourselves."],[21336,21504,"The one with the glasses,"],[21504,21732,"looks like a CEO straight out of a manga."],[21732,21902,"He's like a character come to life."],[21991,22157,"The one in the biker gear,"],[22208,22404,"looks pretty edgy."]],"3":[[481,540,"Mom,"],[540,656,"you just won't give up, will you?"],[657,844,"You found two more dumb women."],[844,877,"I..."],[905,1033,"Just asking for trouble."],[1564,1808,"Who are you calling dumb?"],[2356,2604,"Why is his stare so creepy?"],[2692,2756,"You brat,"],[2780,2856,"watch your mouth."],[2920,3056,"I worked hard to find"],[3056,3216,"daughters-in-law to straighten you two out."],[3560,3780,"Mrs... Mrs. Johnson,"],[3827,4104,"my sister and I are just ordinary people."],[4104,4476,"We probably can't handle these two big shots."],[4588,4888,"We would never take this job."],[5172,5328,"You'd better find someone else."],[5328,5440,"Ahem."],[5692,5744,"$100k."],[6365,6565,"If, within the one-day trial,"],[6596,6904,"you can get Graham to speak,"],[6904,7026,"that's a $100k bonus."],[7078,7292,"If you can keep Colton from fooling around,"],[7292,7424,"that's another $100k."],[7680,7900,"$100k for you, $100k for me."],[7900,8035,"Then the kids at the orphanage"],[8038,8158,"will have enough food."],[8672,8748,"Mom,"],[8764,8864,"are you crazy?"],[8884,8992,"I told you,"],[8992,9084,"what I want is freedom."],[9084,9208,"I'm not getting married!"],[9240,9452,"Marriage means sharing a bed with a woman."],[9468,9596,"Something that gross,"],[9608,9720,"I'll never agree to it."]],"4":[[296,356,"Let's do it."],[372,544,"We'd like to take this job!"],[740,872,"We're signing up to be"],[872,1024,"professional daughters-in-law for the rich."],[1227,1267,"Hmph."],[1556,1671,"You wretched woman."],[1696,1819,"You really don't know your place."],[2060,2248,"Want to be my wife?"],[2428,2523,"Dream on."],[2612,2692,"Let me tell you,"],[2712,2996,"you don't want to mess with me!"],[3815,3864,"She..."],[3864,4039,"How is her grip so strong?"],[4235,4275,"You..."],[4392,4447,"Hey."],[4500,4600,"Let go of my hand!"],[5020,5175,"Back at the orphanage,"],[5180,5488,"I was an expert at handling naughty kids."],[6188,6228,"Mom,"],[6307,6384,"don't worry."],[6400,6720,"I'll make sure he behaves."],[7970,8074,"Hubby,"],[8200,8371,"why haven't you said a word?"],[8392,8515,"Does this mean"],[8528,8740,"you're silently agreeing to marry me?"],[8979,9092,"Shameless woman."],[9215,9312,"Who's your husband?"],[9387,9495,"Who wants to marry you?"],[9623,9720,"So cold."],[9828,9884,"Fine."],[9895,10012,"It's just autism, right?"],[10056,10271,"You don't talk much, but I talk a lot."],[10315,10456,"As long as I'm enthusiastic enough,"],[10456,10735,"I don't believe you'll stay silent forever."],[10971,11095,"These two girls"],[11095,11295,"seem like a perfect match for my sons."],[11423,11500,"Mhm."],[11500,11668,"I really picked the right ones."],[11784,12004,"A mere woman dares to cross me?"],[12048,12204,"Dream on."],[13022,13196,"I'm coming to get you."],[14559,14675,"You stay right here today."],[14717,14843,"Don't go anywhere."]],"5":[[4,124,"You stay right here today."],[156,300,"Don't go anywhere."],[787,851,"You're the only one"],[851,1019,"who's dared to talk to me like that."],[1183,1367,"Don't think just because you're a woman,"],[1396,1591,"that I won't do anything to you!"],[1644,1712,"Colton."],[1792,1935,"Has anyone ever told you"],[1955,2112,"that pointing your finger at others"],[2112,2207,"is really rude?"],[2496,2607,"I'm counting to three."],[2635,2792,"If you don't put it down,"],[3055,3224,"your hand won't be the only thing hurting."],[3411,3475,"Three."],[3588,3667,"Two."],[3903,3952,"One."],[4056,4092,"You"],[4232,4326,"You female hooligan!"],[4424,4515,"Look at yourself."],[4515,4639,"What part of you looks like a woman?"],[4775,4884,"I'm going out"],[4907,4996,"today, for sure!"],[5224,5284,"Fine."],[5352,5428,"Try it, then."],[5564,5700,"You think I scare easily?"],[5764,5867,"Let me tell you,"],[5871,6015,"I've had training."],[6043,6156,"I'm not afraid of you."],[7676,7743,"I"],[7795,7871,"It's not that I can't fight."],[8015,8128,"It's that... good"],[8399,8512,"Good men don't fight women."],[8515,8559,"How about this?"],[8571,8640,"Let's"],[8664,8731,"have a contest."],[8743,8835,"If you win,"],[8920,8987,"I will"],[9035,9087,"marry you."],[9107,9159,"You're on."],[9200,9251,"What's the challenge?"],[9295,9443,"Hmph. Crazy bi*ch."],[9443,9548,"You took the bait."],[9607,9728,"A girl from an orphanage,"],[9740,9868,"who's never seen the world."],[9892,10023,"You think you can peck with me?"],[10131,10231,"Just you wait."],[10307,10400,"I'm going to ruin you."]],"6":[[1532,1600,"This way,"],[1844,1935,"Ms. Collins."],[1935,2000,"This is"],[2000,2080,"Mr. Graham's room."],[2083,2175,"But usually,"],[2183,2267,"he doesn't allow us"],[2267,2383,"to disturb him."],[2516,2600,"Graham,"],[2600,2685,"are you inside?"],[3235,3343,"Didn't hear me?"],[3465,3661,"Graham!"],[3820,4003,"Graham."],[4292,4464,"Oppa."],[4511,4611,"Bro."],[5024,5171,"What a noisy woman."],[5696,5784,"Ignoring me?"],[5811,5888,"Fine."],[5932,6003,"Anyway,"],[6003,6188,"I gave you a heads-up."],[6235,6420,"So don't blame me for"],[6420,6671,"using other methods to get in."],[7356,7443,"Guitar."],[7504,7587,"What do you say?"],[7615,7720,"Do you dare?"],[7879,7968,"Are you sure?"],[8151,8268,"Of course."],[8268,8500,"I've studied music for fifteen years."],[8548,8640,"You think I can't"],[8640,8787,"beat a cheap acrobat like you?"],[9704,9804,"Oh no, this is bad."],[9859,9943,"How could I forget?"],[9943,10023,"Those sisters are"],[10023,10171,"from an orphanage."],[10171,10335,"They probably have no talents."],[10356,10451,"Oh no, oh no."],[10479,10635,"Vivian is definitely going to lose."]],"7":[[68,143,"Which of you"],[180,300,"is going first?"],[587,775,"I don't want anyone saying I bully girls,"],[811,951,"so I'll let you start."],[953,1085,"If you can play even a single tune,"],[1116,1280,"I'll admit defeat."],[1427,1535,"I wouldn't have guessed,"],[1572,1735,"but you're actually quite manly."],[1960,2116,"When you lose later,"],[2132,2316,"don't come crying to beg me."],[5084,5128,"Whoa."],[5196,5335,"You sure look the part."],[5367,5439,"If I didn't know better,"],[5447,5575,"I might've actually been fooled."],[5875,5911,"Alright,"],[5967,6084,"keep quiet."],[6203,6332,"Just let her play."],[7931,8035,"She's so beautiful."],[8035,8135,"She's prettier than any"],[8135,8256,"woman I've ever seen before."],[8384,8447,"Colton,"],[8456,8531,"what are you looking at?"],[8571,8664,"You're gonna lose."],[9504,9600,"Well?"],[9600,9735,"Convinced yet?"],[10335,10428,"I am"],[10428,10531,"a man of honor."],[10531,10631,"I accept my defeat."],[10663,10739,"It's just marriage."],[10768,10848,"I will marry you."],[11404,11500,"Wonderful!"],[11512,11659,"My good-for-nothing youngest son"],[11670,11822,"finally has a taker."],[11833,11945,"This is great!"]],"8":[[320,475,"I gave you a chance."],[475,667,"You didn't answer after three knocks,"],[679,827,"so don't blame me"],[856,995,"for following the rules."],[2255,2383,"Guess she left."],[3044,3123,"Hi."],[3148,3224,"We meet again."],[3239,3396,"Got time for our wedding?"],[4635,4864,"I don't like seeing you hide in the dark."],[4864,5035,"Either get used to the light,"],[5035,5252,"or talk to me."],[5588,5888,"Wow, so beautiful."],[5932,6156,"Did you make all these butterfly specimens?"],[6203,6423,"My sister and I often used to go to the hill"],[6448,6604,"behind the orphanage to catch butterflies."],[6647,6807,"I've seen this kind of butterfly."],[6821,6993,"They always fly towards the light."],[8243,8364,"But I think"],[8364,8540,"live Blue Morphos chasing the light"],[8556,8700,"look much better than being pinned here."],[8807,8915,"Just like you."],[9192,9287,"I know you can hear me."],[10084,10268,"I knew nothing was playing."],[10479,10592,"What are you doing?"],[10592,10723,"Angry already?"],[10740,10992,"I just put on your headphones for a sec."],[10992,11179,"Besides, I didn't say anything bad."],[11179,11304,"Lame."],[11331,11459,"You won't say a single word."],[11459,11584,"If I marry you,"],[11584,11692,"I'd probably die of boredom."],[11768,12071,"But it's not a bad deal for me."],[12148,12304,"Judging by your looks,"],[12376,12600,"you must be..."],[12815,12887,"You"],[12980,13075,"How can there be"],[13075,13156,"such a vulgar woman?"]],"9":[[479,716,"I didn't think a mute like you kept pets."],[856,924,"Wait, no."],[964,1180,"Don't tell me you want to make it a specimen."],[1288,1396,"You can't do that."],[1400,1519,"Bunnies are so cute."],[1532,1671,"Obviously, they should be made into"],[1683,1816,"Spicy Rabbit Heads,"],[1839,1971,"or Braised Rabbit with Corn."],[2087,2187,"I still think"],[2187,2355,"Spicy Rabbit Heads taste the best."],[2428,2744,"Drenched in sauce, and then crunch!"],[3055,3128,"Nora."],[3176,3235,"Are you even human?"],[3279,3379,"You spoke!"],[3488,3671,"You spoke!"],[3671,3864,"Hundred grand! Hundred grand! Hundred grand!"],[3925,4061,"Get the hell out right now."],[4090,4258,"I won't marry you,"],[4279,4356,"because"],[4361,4453,"I'm allergic to women."],[4856,5088,"Seriously?"],[5107,5307,"If I touch you and nothing happens,"],[5307,5396,"we're getting married."],[5430,5502,"Deal?"],[6307,6392,"What allergy?"],[6423,6564,"See? Nothing happened."],[6756,6979,"Normally, physical contact with women"],[6979,7123,"makes me break out in a rash."],[7123,7240,"Why not with her?"],[7464,7723,"Oh, thank heavens!"],[7723,7904,"My son finally spoke!"],[8007,8228,"Picking these two sisters as daughters-in-law"],[8228,8415,"was the right decision after all."]],"10":[[851,1008,"Happy wedding!"],[1758,1964,"Nora is nothing but a freak of nature"],[1964,2087,"who barely qualifies as a woman."],[2103,2267,"She's louder than a hundred parrots."],[2367,2483,"I only came here because she tricked me."],[2507,2612,"As for me,"],[2660,2800,"I was also tricked by"],[2800,2902,"that lunatic, Vivian."],[3000,3139,"I didn't want to get married."],[3307,3503,"I... I don't want to get married at all!"],[4100,4260,"Congratulations to the four of you."],[4306,4462,"You are the first and second"],[4475,4584,"couples of the month."],[4628,4779,"Your love will last a lifetime,"],[4803,4903,"and your home"],[4903,5000,"will be full of children."],[5339,5420,"Thanks."],[6324,6564,"We're rich! We're rich!"],[6564,6859,"Let's go home and get the money!"],[6878,7210,"Who wants an eternity with this lunatic?"],[7442,7645,"Let's take a photo."],[8252,8320,"We are"],[8328,8435,"the world's number one"],[8435,8671,"best, best, best, best, best!"],[10471,10735,"Congratulations on passing your probation"],[10735,10992,"and officially becoming my daughters-in-law."],[11176,11359,"Here is the $200,000 bonus"],[11359,11456,"we agreed on earlier."],[12268,12392,"From now on,"],[12392,12471,"I'll deposit $100,000"],[12471,12587,"into your bank accounts every month."],[12676,12731,"You two,"],[12731,12900,"just need to settle down here"],[12900,13096,"and keep my two sons in line."],[13152,13228,"Yes, ma'am!"],[13228,13380,"Mission accepted!"],[13536,13700,"Even though your marriage to my sons"],[13700,13847,"is by contract,"],[13847,14152,"you still get the customary gold jewelry."],[14152,14259,"Everything is here."],[14259,14443,"Quick, see if you like it."],[14589,14744,"Wow!"],[14875,14943,"Sister,"],[14952,15063,"being a professional daughter-in-law"],[15063,15300,"is way better than early retirement."],[15300,15463,"As long as they don't go bankrupt,"],[15463,15684,"I could do this job forever."],[15712,15819,"That's good."],[15819,16008,"Tonight is your wedding night."],[16028,16212,"I've already had someone prepare"],[16212,16312,"the bridal suite."],[16312,16380,"You two"],[16380,16515,"should turn in early."],[16515,16624,"What?"],[16624,16728,"We have to consummate the marriage?"],[16880,16996,"Consummate?"],[17020,17220,"That wasn't in the contract."]],"11":[[20,119,"Consummate?"],[124,300,"That wasn't in the contract."],[391,540,"It wasn't in the contract,"],[548,608,"but"],[651,724,"since you've already"],[724,811,"gotten your marriage licenses,"],[835,891,"don't you"],[919,996,"want to tame"],[996,1100,"these two brats?"],[1359,1575,"And secure your place in the Johnson family?"],[2251,2360,"These two sons of mine,"],[2383,2492,"are a lost cause."],[2835,2907,"If"],[2907,3080,"you can give me some grandchildren"],[3155,3275,"and raise them to be successful,"],[3321,3503,"then everything the Johnsons own"],[3535,3684,"will eventually be yours."],[3820,3900,"Sister,"],[3924,4120,"so she wants to groom the grandchildren"],[4139,4292,"as her sons are useless."],[4311,4456,"As long as we please her,"],[4589,4733,"we don't have to wait on our husbands,"],[4747,4879,"and we still get paid every month."],[4971,5139,"Being a professional daughter-in-law"],[5339,5435,"has way better perks"],[5435,5588,"than a corporate job!"],[5952,6039,"Exactly."],[6084,6132,"Mhm."],[6320,6579,"Who knew that after a decade in an orphanage,"],[6628,6715,"the luckiest girl alive"],[6748,6868,"would turn out to be me."],[6892,6956,"Mhm."],[7248,7295,"Mom,"],[7371,7440,"don't worry."],[7464,7548,"Tonight,"],[7559,7728,"we guarantee to complete the mission!"],[7831,7895,"Good."],[8000,8051,"You psycho,"],[8079,8148,"don't even think about it."],[8192,8312,"I'm never gonna"],[8331,8404,"touch you."],[9156,9256,"What's going on?"],[9276,9392,"Why am I so nervous"],[9451,9576,"when she is getting close?"],[9884,10068,"You actually look pretty good."],[10171,10312,"Having a baby with you,"],[10331,10423,"wouldn't be so bad."],[10471,10571,"However,"],[10607,10748,"seeing how resistant you are"],[10748,10835,"to having a baby,"],[10943,11192,"don't tell me you're"],[11295,11343,"gay?"],[11448,11535,"What are you saying?"],[11623,11671,"I"],[11671,11728,"Let me tell you,"],[11748,11848,"I'm in perfect health."],[11895,11976,"Seven times a night is no problem."],[12231,12323,"It's just that,"],[12363,12468,"I have no interest"],[12479,12852,"in an \"unprecedented\" woman"],[12884,12952,"like you."],[13147,13319,"\"Unprecedented\"?"],[13591,13636,"Yeah."],[13696,13752,"That's right."],[13884,13947,"Forget it."],[13996,14047,"I"],[14063,14156,"have no time for this."],[14215,14324,"I'm going to write songs."],[14415,14463,"I'm off."],[14684,14719,"I"],[15671,15740,"Hubby."]],"12":[[56,115,"Hubby."],[167,291,"Your brother can't perform."],[379,512,"You shouldn't have"],[579,687,"that problem, right?"],[1082,1272,"Your chest is rock hard."],[1306,1424,"Other places"],[1480,1623,"shouldn't be soft either, right?"],[1760,1932,"Making babies won't be a problem, will it?"],[2912,3000,"Vivian, Nora."],[3060,3171,"My two sons,"],[3235,3320,"one loves"],[3320,3388,"show business,"],[3388,3471,"involved in scandals,"],[3600,3692,"and neglects his proper duties."],[3703,3784,"The other"],[3827,3943,"doesn't talk much,"],[3960,4015,"but,"],[4032,4124,"he's innocent."],[4259,4363,"He hasn't really"],[4376,4504,"spent much time with girls."],[4611,4675,"From now on,"],[4724,4775,"I'm"],[4792,4896,"entrusting the"],[5067,5192,"two of them to you."],[5447,5511,"Mm-hmm."],[5732,5780,"Mom,"],[5788,5843,"don't worry."],[5862,6000,"As long as the money is right,"],[6024,6100,"we sisters"],[6120,6296,"will do this job perfectly."],[6328,6388,"That's right."],[6409,6531,"Tonight,"],[6531,6676,"we'll definitely have"],[6676,6895,"a wonderful wedding night with them."],[7007,7087,"Good, good, good."],[7121,7312,"I'll go check on your"],[7312,7379,"bridal suite."],[7379,7431,"Mm."],[8284,8335,"Brother."],[8392,8423,"Mm."],[8448,8504,"You saw it."],[8584,8671,"Those two women"],[8692,8771,"married into"],[8771,8920,"our family just for the money."],[9312,9379,"I think they're"],[9379,9479,"celebrating too early."],[9568,9640,"Sooner or later,"],[9679,9831,"I'm divorcing that crazy woman."],[9940,10079,"She even wants a child with me."],[10159,10240,"Tonight,"],[10359,10512,"I'm kicking her out of this house."],[11160,11240,"Hubby!"]],"13":[[967,1043,"Nora."],[1043,1080,"Yeah?"],[1151,1296,"The Johnson brothers"],[1335,1535,"don't look easy to handle."],[1619,1744,"Especially your husband."],[1848,1967,"He looks like"],[2023,2148,"he's mentally unstable."],[2207,2307,"You'd better be careful."],[2419,2496,"Really?"],[2564,2667,"I actually think"],[2692,2864,"he's cold on the outside, warm on the inside,"],[2927,3096,"strong and fit,"],[3096,3200,"and easy to handle."],[3600,3800,"