You're not even fit to tie his shoes."],[6735,6868,"Stop daydreaming."],[7220,7335,"I am his wife."],[7348,7498,"I sleep in his arms every night."],[7512,7643,"Why would I need to dream?"],[7660,7848,"You're Mr. Johnson's wife?"],[8095,8184,"Nora,"],[8207,8343,"you're getting more ridiculous by the second."],[8443,8579,"I think you've lost your mind!"],[8677,8721,"Security!"],[8735,8807,"Where is security?!"],[8840,8900,"Take this woman"],[8900,8968,"and throw her out!"],[9279,9344,"What are you doing?"],[9390,9471,"Director Quinn,"],[9528,9592,"I'd advise you"],[9592,9700,"not to act rashly."],[9723,9856,"She's not someone you can afford to offend."],[9868,9935,"Avery Hughes."],[9948,10040,"This is the Design Department,"],[10071,10200,"and you have no say here."],[10219,10320,"Get her out of here, now!"],[10600,10676,"Stop!"],[10764,10840,"Mr. Johnson is here."],[10859,10959,"Just wait to eat your words."]],"40":[[12,88,"Mr. Johnson is here."],[108,204,"Just wait to eat your words."],[374,420,"Mr. Johnson,"],[440,620,"this woman doesn't know her place."],[628,708,"She's impersonating your wife."],[741,869,"I was about to teach her a lesson."],[1311,1403,"You want to teach her a lesson?"],[1488,1564,"Yes."],[1575,1639,"Who knows"],[1639,1732,"who she slept with to"],[1732,1823,"get into this company."],[1883,1948,"I"],[2039,2144,"I'm sorry about that."],[2355,2476,"Graham..."],[2476,2616,"Is he concerned about me?"],[3279,3338,"Mr. Johnson,"],[3407,3556,"what are you doing?"],[3967,4120,"As you can see,"],[4132,4247,"Nora"],[4247,4371,"is my newlywed wife."],[4428,4592,"She's your wife?"],[4635,4832,"She's just a pretty face."],[4837,5051,"She has no education or background."],[5055,5167,"How could you let her be"],[5167,5274,"your wife?"],[5384,5507,"I'm doomed."],[5520,5624,"I must have humiliated"],[5624,5735,"Graham."],[5767,5915,"If they find out"],[5924,6020,"I used those tricks"],[6020,6139,"to marry into the Johnsons,"],[6146,6306,"will Graham"],[6339,6473,